txt.en: 'Only a matter of time before they come back, but you sure scared the feathers off 'em. If those birds are smart enough, they'll think twice now!'
'These cursed sea-gulls never give me a moment's rest!\n\n'Shoo 'em away from Melgobas, and I'll pay you!'
You've scared off the sea-gulls... for now.\n\nYou should let Rindur know. He can be found in Melgobas.
Rindur fishes for the people of Melgobas, not the local sea-gulls!
Hungry sea-gulls flock to Melgobas to steal Rindur's hard-earned fish.\n\nYou should shoo them away.
